title: It’s Not Just MVDP and Mads: Here Are 5 Outsiders for Paris-Roubaix
content:
From a super-size sprinter to a returning cobblestone specialist, here are the riders that could cause havoc in the men's race though 'Hell'.

Read the full article at It’s Not Just MVDP and Mads: Here Are 5 Outsiders for Paris-Roubaix on Velo.
author: Jim Cotton
